Summary: Took 3 pictures and this UFO appeared in two of them
divs: Sighting DetailsSitting in my house, looked out at the clouds and decided to take a couple of pictures of the sky since it looked like a severe storm was about to errupt. I took two pictures and then looked at my digital camera and saw this item in them. I took a third picture and it did not appear. I didn't have any idea what this was but when I put pictures on my computer and enlarged them it doesn't appear to be anything I can figure out. I didn't see this item until I looked at the pictures so I don't know where it came from or where it went. These three pictures were taken within seconds of each other.
